        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownDawnstarFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionDawnstar\")",
        "content": "Leigelf owns the Quicksilver Mine on Dawnstar's east end. Estranged husband of Beitild — they keep competing mines, competing households, and an ongoing feud the whole town can hear.",
        "display_name": "Leigelf - Quicksilver Mine",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.7,
