        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownDawnstarFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionDawnstar\")",
        "content": "Silus Vesuius runs the small Mythic Dawn museum in Dawnstar — his ancestors were part of the cult that killed Emperor Uriel Septim. He's been gathering fragments of Mehrunes' Razor.",
